{"type":"message","id":"e25b65f2","parentId":"b5d4a82f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:00:44.388Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me analyze what needs to change in MEMORY.md:\n\n**New signal from Apr 6 daily file:**\n1. **GitHub Skills Upload:** 35 skill repos on github.com/Icattj (later renamed from openclaw-skill-* to clean names). Total 42 repos.\n2. **Pangkas v1.3:** Barbershop POS app live at /pangkas/, GitHub: Icattj/pangkas. Key features: discount chips, quick reorder, 7-day revenue chart, bottom nav.\n3. **Deep Think System:** Connected WA → MAGI Deep Think API. Multi-round debate (1-7 rounds), intensity 10. Scripts: ~/bin/magi-deep-think.py, ~/bin/push-deep-think.py.\n4. **Security Hardening (Apr 6):** CouchDB, Sentra AI, Crucix, DnD all bound to 127.0.0.1. Only SSH, Caddy, OpenClaw exposed.\n5. **New Installations:** Camoufox + GMaps scraper, Crucix OSINT dashboard, qmd local search (164 vault files indexed).\n6. **Repo Audit:** 4 agents evaluated 27 repos → 6 IMPLEMENT, 6 LATER, 6 REFERENCE, 7 DELETE.\n7. **Lessons learned:** Module scope vs inline onclick in MAGI, sub-agent timeouts on large files, copy proven design > generate from scratch.\n8. **GitHub PAT:** stored in ~/.credentials/github-token.\n9. **Website Builder:** Planned but not yet built.\n10. **Shannon Security:** Setup started but not completed.\n11. **Skill repos renamed:** All 33 from openclaw-skill-* to clean names.\n12. **bilibili-reader and xiaohongshu-reader deleted** from skills (Chinese-specific, not needed).\n\n**What needs updating in MEMORY.md:**\n- Add Pangkas project to Active Projects\n- Add GitHub presence (42 repos, skills published)\n- Add Deep Think integration notes to MAGI v2 Features\n- Update Security section (hardening done Apr 6)\n- Add Website Builder to Pending\n- Add lessons about module scope and sub-agent timeouts\n- Update Skills section (remove bilibili/xiaohongshu, note GitHub publication)\n- Add Crucix OSINT and qmd to infrastructure\n- Remove or update items that are now resolved\n\n**Stale/outdated items to check:**\n- \"Richard account deletion pending\" — still pending, keep\n- \"WhatsApp flapping\" — last mentioned Apr 5-6, still unresolved, keep\n- \"Gmail login blocked\" — still pending, keep\n\n**Lines management:** Currently 128 lines, target < 200. With new additions, I'll need to be efficient.\n\nLet me also check if there are any files older than 90 days to archive:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_FsvVldI4hbppeYftGwxXsa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\ncutoff = datetime(2026, 4, 7) - timedelta(days=90)\nprint(f'Cutoff date: {cutoff.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\")}')\n# Files before 2026-01-07 should be archived\n\""}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":818,"cacheRead":38554,"cacheWrite":435,"totalTokens":39808,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.02045,"cacheRead":0.019277,"cacheWrite":0.0027187500000000002,"total":0.04245075}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775530821350}}
